{"type": "article", "id": 9777, "title": "Airbnb 泰晤士河水上漂浮", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-20T07:12:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155852ye10g6XJKRT542Pq.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"s1\">Airbnb 近日推出了一个“水上漂浮屋”，位置是英国的泰晤士河上，屋子里设有一间客厅，两间卧室以及洗手间。而室外则有一座小花园，一个狗屋和一棵苹果树。这意味着，你甚至可以带上你的小狗去泰晤士河上发呆了。小屋将会从 5 月 22 日开始沿着泰晤士河一路漂流。</span>\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155848uo5XJ2wZT7iYAO9H.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155848ZMnfQXLKUj9RiFao.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155849sv2IocWbeRtNaLp5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155850GvqA4LrlopIkJxg7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155850YktZPi25RGoJTgE8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155851qXMLknBJhpzsdc3Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155851X3ju8UWGSxIcZ5nh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n\t</p>\r\n\n\n"}